Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提高退休年齡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raising the age of retirement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是對美國夢不可容忍的侵蝕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is an unacceptable erosion of the American Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果共和黨無法通過福利改革\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the Republicans fail to pass a reasonable Omnibus package
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達成合理的綜合解決方案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by demanding entitlement reform,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會迫使聯邦政府凍結開銷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they will force the federal government into a spending freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凍瘡會長在他們手上  不是我們手上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The frostbite will be on their hands. Not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句是不是有點過了  凍瘡那句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think that's a bit much? The frostbite bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是國情諮文  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it's the State of the Union, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想爭取中部各州的贊同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want to appeal to the flyover states.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會喜歡那句話的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll like that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要點更有力的句子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want something more forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們手上沾滿血\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Blood on their hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們丟回冰河紀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Throw us back into the ice age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡那句  克里斯蒂娜  我們試試\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like that, Christina. Let's try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達  克里斯蒂娜  你也過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda. Christina, you come up here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上有兩種副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are two types of vice presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受氣包和鬥牛士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doormats and matadors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我想做那種呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which do you think I intend to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在為內政操心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's hung up on the domestic agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句關於中國的話也沒說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not a single word about China.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的直覺是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His instincts are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果政府在演講後第二天關門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the government shuts down one day after the speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他講了什麼就完全不重要了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not a single word in the speech matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得馬上解決凍結開銷的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to address the freeze now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國的事得靠後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}China comes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩黨為了改革的事吵了幾個月了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Both parties have been wrangling over entitlements for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來三天裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What makes you think a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能出現奇蹟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is gonna happen in the next three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給共和黨他們想要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We give the Republicans exactly what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退休年齡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Retirement age?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可跨越的界限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a line in the sand we cannot cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最終還是得跨  所以何必爭下去呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We will cross it eventually, so why keep fighting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以推動參議院通過法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can push this through the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我做到  總統就能在國情諮文中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And once I do, the president will announce
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈兩黨達成了一項重要協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a major bipartisan agreement in the State of the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們避免了政府關門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We avoid a government shutdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而功勞歸白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the White House gets credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太冒險了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a huge risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失敗  會顏面掃地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if it fails, a huge embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是丟我的臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The embarrassment will be entirely my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事我來擔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  也不好說服總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even so, the president is gonna require some serious persuasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟他談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm happy to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別  我來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. No. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友去說  他更容易接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll be more amenable if it comes from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  可信的密友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're right. A trusted confidant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去試試水吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me test the waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克黨  成員  一人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Cult of Tusk. Membership: one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個信徒恰好是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that one disciple just so happens to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由世界最有權力的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the most powerful man in the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少目前還是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For now.
