Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福利改革  把退休年齡提到67歲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The entitlements. Raising the age of eligibility to 67.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們那邊不會同意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your people will never go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層同意  他們就會點頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They will if the leadership does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而領導層會同意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the leadership will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒斷奶時這事就是兩黨的爭議焦點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They fought us on this since I was in diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我能說服我黨同意提高退休年齡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Assuming that I can get this past my people and convince them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能說服你那邊嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}can you convince yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很困難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a tough sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是參議院多數黨領袖  赫克特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're the Senate majority leader, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要遊說  可以直接命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to sell. You can dictate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼回報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you want in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個正常運轉的政府  避免開銷凍結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A working government. We stave off the freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在《教育法案》上贏了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You won on education.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們讓你當上了副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We confirmed you as vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨需要贏一次  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Republicans need a win, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在提供贏的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's what I'm offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在福利改革上贏了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You get a win on entitlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們避免了關門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We avoid a shutdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩黨合作  雙方都得分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone gets points for bipartisanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我擔心誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know who I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯·哈斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curtis Haas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個麻煩  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a troublemaker, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還控制了你三分之一的黨內成員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who controls a third of your caucus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他絕不會同意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he'll never go for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就想看民主黨不好過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wants to see the Democrats suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他考慮一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just bring him to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只求這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋拉格小姐  我叫盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Miss Gallagher? My name is Lucas Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是《華盛頓先驅報》的副主編\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a deputy editor at the Washington Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德溫先生  拜託了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Goodwin, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需要幾分鐘  我不求別的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just a few moments. That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想跟你說話  就會回你的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I wanted to talk to you, I would have returned your calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讀過我的郵件嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you read my emails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀了  所以我沒聯繫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. Which is why I didn't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我個機會解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me a chance to walk you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕回白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to get back to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -彼得·羅素是被殺害的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry. - Peter Russo was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊·巴恩斯也是  我跟她是同事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So was Zoe Barnes. I was working with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口  聽我說...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop and listen --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·安德伍德是幕後黑手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood is the one who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  這是一派胡言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen! This is nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒駕記錄  聽證會  所有都是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The DUI. The brack hearing. All of it was part of --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再這樣了  好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This has to stop. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德找過你了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Underwood talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-讓你不要和別人說這些事嗎  -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Tell you not to speak with anybody? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格·斯坦普嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論你以為發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼讓你這樣跟蹤我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whatever compelled you to stalk me like this --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一可能知道點什麼的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're the only person who might know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能理解得了的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who could understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有別人可以說這事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got -- I've got no one else I can talk --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解  也不想理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't understand. And I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎  這裡面沒什麼內情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay? There's no story here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  只要五分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, just five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想你自己的行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just think about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守在樓外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Waiting outside of a building --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是弗蘭克·安德伍德  彼得可能還活著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Peter would still be alive if it wasn't for Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了很大力氣忘記彼得的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've worked really hard to put Peter behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我再看到你  你再來找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So if I see you again, if I hear from you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不僅會報警\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll not only contact the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會讓副總統知道你在對他說三道四\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let the vice president know what you're saying about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就等著特勤局來找上門吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and then you can deal with the Secret Service, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是正常的海外聲音  中國那邊有些雜音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the usual overseas chatter. Bit of a bum in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們覺得原因在貿易緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we chalk that up to the trade tensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特勤局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統和副總統收到的死亡威脅數正常\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Average number of death threats to both POTUS and the VP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都交給了聯調局的好夥伴們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We passed them along to our dear friends at the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯調局呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯調局向我們特勤局的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The FBI confirms the level of activity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好夥伴們確認了活動程度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of our dear friends at the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們全部進行了追蹤調查  沒有高階別的威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We followed up on everything. No high-level threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有需要直接\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So nothing we need to report directly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向總統和副總統彙報的內容嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to the president or vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有  -謝謝  先生們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No. - Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你發的郵件還有別人看過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The email you sent. Has anyone else seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了告知我的特工外  沒有了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except for the agent that alerted me, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他機構可能會偶然看到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Other agencies might have stumbled upon this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  他們大概也不會在意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even so, they probably ignored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道是誰發的帖子嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any idea who's making the posts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深網論壇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Deep Web forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎無法追蹤  很可能就是一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Almost impossible to trace. Lone wolf most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你找到這個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得有對生命構成直接威脅的證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need a direct threat to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統剛剛上任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president just assumed office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這類陰謀論絕不能甚囂塵上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't have this conspiracy stuff going mainstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這類傳言一般會漸漸平息  -我不能冒這個險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- This sort of thing usually fizzles out -- - I can't take the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去找到這個人  把他關起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to find him and put him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他並沒犯罪  -但他有這個傾向\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- He hasn't committed a crime. - But he wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來個推波助瀾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要耗費人力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That requires manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手裡有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've got men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會暴露我的  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It exposes me, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直給你透露訊息  因為你是老朋友了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've always kept you informed because you're an old pal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你  但...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I trust you. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要我展開正式行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking about an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你在白宮工作的老朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm an old pal who now works at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老朋友之間說說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Between old pals,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個行政部門聯絡官已經當得太久了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been stuck as the executive liaison for way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是否擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How worried are you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您所在社羣的學校內會發生大規模槍擊事件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that a mass shooting could happen in a school in your community?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常擔心  比較擔心  不怎麼擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Great deal, somewhat, not so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不擔心  還是不確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not at all, unsure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音很性感嘛  人怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You sound hot. Are you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比較性感  非常性感\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Somewhat hot? A great deal hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}掛斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}林奇堡兒童醫院  電話  傳真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是林奇堡兒童醫院小兒科\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lynchburg Children's, Pediatric Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找謝莉爾·波斯納\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I talk to Cheryl Posner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  她正在值班\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry. She's on duty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是她女兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold on one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  瑞秋嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel? Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜心  你在聽嗎  請別...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sweetheart, are you there? Please, do--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}掛斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好  傑伊先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello, Mr. Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My name is Rachel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表全國槍支教育中心向您致電\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I'm calling on behalf of the National Firearm Education Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您能和我簡單聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you be able to speak with me briefly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您對槍支立法和第二修正案的看法嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}regarding firearm legislation and Second Amendment legislation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是薇拉力薦的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, you're Willa's top choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我丈夫和我為什麼要選擇你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why should you be my husband's and my top choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在過去十年中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Over the past 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你們夫婦的報道加起來還不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the two of you combined have gotten less coverage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內布拉斯加州資淺眾議員的平均水平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than the average junior congressman from Nebraska.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想太受矚目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't seek the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說你們非要如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not suggesting you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我沒猜錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But am I correct in assuming
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫會是一位行事積極的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that your husband will be an active vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓媒體不去關注積極的副總統是比較難的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's harder to keep an active VP out of the press than in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們可以讓媒體剛好有些料可追\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it's possible if we give the media just enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不至於什麼都拿不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to keep them from starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪長大的  康納\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where'd you grow up, Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德州  和你一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Texas. Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達拉斯嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dallas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉布克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lubbock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想改口音可比你們難多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had a much thicker accent to get rid of you than y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我有口音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you know I had one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倆第一次共同接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your first joint interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,86年你丈夫競選州議員時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when your husband was running for state assembly in '86.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網上有嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's on the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我聯繫了格林維爾當地的電視臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. No. I contacted the local affiliate in Greenville.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不願郵寄錄影帶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They wouldn't send me the tapes via mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就親自去資料庫看了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so I went down there and watched in their vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到南卡羅萊納嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To South Carolina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應聘就得做好準備工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I want a job, I do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很期待你的表現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I look forward to seeing what you come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  安德伍德太太\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,週四見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼能算勝利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't see how this is a victory for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要麼面臨開銷凍結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our choices are the freeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主黨會為這個飽受責難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which the Democrats get blamed for, or --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一定  共和...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not necessarily. The Republi--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一樣會受責難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, which we definitely get blamed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要麼給他們  -福利改革嗎  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Or we offer them -- - Entitlements, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經表了態  不能回頭了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We took a stand. We can't turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧可讓政府停轉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd rather see the government grind to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果頭條是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Think of the headline:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《民主黨高層通過法案  避免開銷凍結》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Democrat Leadership Enacts Entitlement Reform, Staves Off Freeze."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是團結和進步的表現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We show unity. We offer progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說服幾個中堅保守派吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's convert some lifelong conservatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門多薩答應合作了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have Mendoza's assurance he'll work with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想把頭伸出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to put our necks out there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等人家落刀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just to have the guillotine fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  我們也會一起伸出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You won't. My neck will be right out there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯暈血\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis faints at the sight of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會允許他們割傷他的面板的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'd never let them break the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬團結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  別這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no, no. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉瑞  能來一趟嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Larry, can you come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我電腦不知道怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something weird's going on with my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我修好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing. It's fine. Uh, I fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你要的我能給你  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠革新\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not as progressive as I'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夠極端吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退休年齡升到67歲  2055年前政府都能負擔福利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raising retirement age to 67 makes entitlements solvent until 2055.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能省一萬億\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it saves us over a trillion dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不花納稅人的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without a single penny of taxpayer income.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改到68歲能再省三千億\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}68 would give us another 300 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想禁止提前退休\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'd like to eliminate early retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全禁止嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Entirely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,68歲退  64歲早退呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about 68 and 64?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要對選民負責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a responsibility to my constituents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承諾過某些問題絕不妥協\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promised I wouldn't waver when it comes to things --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}民共兩黨票數僵持時  茶黨的傾向能決定局勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要讓茶黨決定財政立法嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are we really going to allow the Tea Party to determine fiscal legislation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒指望他們幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never been beholden to the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧  柯蒂斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有茶黨政治行動委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't have won reelection
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你的一千萬  你也贏不了重選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if their PACs hadn't dumped 10 million into your campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們對縮減開支的看法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If their definition of budgetary conservatism
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我不謀而合  那就正好...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}happens to overlap with mine, that's a function--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯  柯蒂斯  友善一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curtis. Curtis. Let's show some goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,68歲和64歲可以接受嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you stomach 68 and 64?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上生效嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Effective immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五年以後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Five years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能突然拋出這個提議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you know we can't throw this on people without any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得給他們時間消化\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They need some time to digest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  就是不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I just can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  回去跟你們的幕僚和同事商量一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Meet with your staff. Consult with your colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去商量  明天再談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll consult with mine. And let's talk tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. I can agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這第一步很不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But this is a good first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修正案通過後  法案進行表決時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do we make sure Curtis can't filibuster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯阻撓議事怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when we get the amendment passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能走到那步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Assuming we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只跟你說  我覺得我們可以改變他的想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Between you and me, I'm sure we can turn him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想冒險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just want to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們讓修正案的表決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We make sure the passage of the amendment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為法案表決的一部分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}constitutes the passage of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事先約定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}By previous agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  修正案一通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's right. We pass the amendment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就完事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and then we're done. Wham, bam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能落到紙上嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we put that in writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓艾瑞克森找我吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have Erikson reach out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Muchos gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}開啟我  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good evening, Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著麥克風說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Speak into the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,返回主屏  開啟另一個應用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go to the home screen. Open the other app.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先告訴我你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你調查過我  想必已經知道我是誰了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've done your research. You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道那是不是你的真實身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I know who you claim to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是現在還不相信我  那就不必談了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you're not convinced by now, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別別\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽你的  我返回主屏了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, I'm on the home screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟驗證程式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Open the notary app.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確保你不為執法部門工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To ensure you aren't law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm -- I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就簽了它\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼簽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的拇指按在攝像頭上  然後點"掃描"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold your thumb to the camera and press "Capture."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}身份驗證  指紋掃描
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一你是給執法部門的呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do I know you're not law enforcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼簽了這檔案  要麼走人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sign the document or walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}身份驗證  指紋掃描
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我簽好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點"發送"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Press "Send."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發送到哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is this going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用了伊朗和其他12個國家的代理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm VPNing through Iran and 12 other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心  連結很安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. It's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要《華盛頓先驅報》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need the two-step verification code
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內部伺服器的兩步驗證碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the Herald's internal servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不知道該怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I don't -- I don't even know how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然知道  看你的郵箱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do. Check your email.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這平板毀了  尤其要把產品序列號抹乾淨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Destroy the iPad, especially the serial number
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郵件記牢之後就刪掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and delete the email after you've memorized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  還在聽嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  弗蘭克  我還以為看到了一只印加地鳩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Frank. I -- I thought I saw an Inca dove.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是冬遷飛錯方向了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Must have flown the wrong direction for winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊好像風挺大  你在哪呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It sounds windy. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我家樓頂  裝了個野鳥餵食器\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Top of my building. Got a bird feeder up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統的工作做得不錯  聽說他同意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nice work with the President. I hear we have a green light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一開始也不願意  但還是讓步了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He pushed back in the beginning, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的寫手正在改講稿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His writers are reworking the speech now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也快成了  五年後  68退休  64早退\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm very close to a deal.  68/64 in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按說好的削減開支\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Spending cuts as discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說定了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that rock solid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就差握手簽字了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Soon as we shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰在作梗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's the hold-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯·哈斯  不過也在意料之中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curtis Haas, which isn't a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過會兒就和他見面  他是最後的障礙了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm meeting with him soon. He's the final hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間掐得太正好了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cutting it pretty close, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是歷史性的時刻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, this is -- this is historic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約翰遜當總統時共和黨人就想推動福利改革了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Republicans have wanted entitlement reform since Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯會同意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curtis will come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外我們得在講稿裡提到延遲退休的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the meantime we should get the new retirement age into the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是別說得太詳細  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would stay away from the specifics, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算參議院通過了  眾議院沒準也...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, I-- even if it passes, the House might--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對眾議院的瞭解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the House better
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你對鳥深入得多  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than you know birds, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  他們肯定會通過參議院的版本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Believe me when I say they'll pass the Senate version.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟總統說說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這事絕不能有差錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just make sure this is airtight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你  什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先驅報的那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From the Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定在和佐伊一起調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He must have been working with Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much does he know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會比她多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No more than she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道的可不少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She knew enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在辦  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有證據嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局面在控制中  我只是想告訴你一聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's under control. I just thought you should be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟總統  共和黨和塔斯克周旋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm juggling the President, the Republicans, Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不能...  -你就繼續忙你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I can't -- - And you should stay focused on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德溫交給我處理  你無須擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodwin's on my plate. Not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到20世紀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It wasn't until the 20th century
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客觀主義理念才成為主流觀念\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that the notion of noble objectivism came into the forefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事實就是事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But facts are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1992年  事實  有人拿出一張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}1992. Fact: George Bush, Sr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老布什詢問售貨掃描機是如何工作的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is shown asking how a grocery scanner works,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進而攻擊他無知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he gets nailed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相是  他們向他展示的是一個新模型機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fact? They were showing him a new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是在問新機器與舊機器的差別\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was asking how the new one was different than the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇而已  並非無知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curiosity, not ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但語境的缺失卻傳達了一個更有衝擊力的觀點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But the lack of context told a more powerful narrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在對事實的諸多整理中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no arrangement of acts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪個是...完全客觀的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that is, uh, purely objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們總算可以做點什麼了  終於有手段了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can finally do something. We have the means to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個毛都沒長全的少年黑客...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some teenage pimple-faced hacker --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是很高階的入侵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This was a sophisticated infiltration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩子做得出來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not the work of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  郵件在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look. Here's the email.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機器人希洛尼摩斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hieronymus Bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}希洛尼摩斯  古希臘史學家  以公正著名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦調查局已經追捕他很多年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The FBI's been hunting him for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯  聽我說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas, listen to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們拿到了這些記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we get these records,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你幫忙理順時間先後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll need your help tracking timelines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼湊整件事的發展...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}piecing together the chronology of the --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你只想找個人安慰你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. You want somebody to hold your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你  做這些無用功沒什麼不對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and say it's okay to go on this fucking goose chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不該在伊薩卡教書  你的能力不止如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be teaching in Ithaca. You're better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你該回華盛頓  -我就該待在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You should be back home -- - I belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一群宿醉未消的英語專業大學生嘮叨嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Droning on to a bunch of hungover English majors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對真相的看法是錯的  客觀事實是存在的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're wrong about the truth. There is objective truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他殺了她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know it's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實就是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽最多只剩10到15年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My mom has 10, 15 years left at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我畢業後加起來也沒有上個月跟她相處時間久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've seen her more in the past month than since I left for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡更簡單  也很安靜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's simpler here. It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要這樣的環境  她需要我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need that. She needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我那晚做出了那樣的反應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry that night how I reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾你失去了你的女友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry you lost your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾世界就是這麼操蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry the world is this fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我幫不了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人在哪裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天給你幫了個倒忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did you a disservice yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該在整個領導層面前讓你為難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We shouldn't have put you on the spot in front of all the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐  柯蒂斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have a seat, Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道你必須堅守立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We know that you have an obligation to take a firm stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但承諾福利改革是你競選的核心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but entitlement reform is something you ran on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在唾手可得了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and now it's within your grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說說你的顧慮吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So tell us your fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顧慮就是共和黨又會贏一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That the Democrats get another win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在中期選舉中失利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We suffer in the midterms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一屆國會就會廢除協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the next Congress dismantles the agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們在玩花招\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think we're being disingenuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的選民不信任政府\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My constituents don't trust the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓他們覺得我們受到了矇騙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't have them thinking the wool's been pulled over our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我所料  赫克特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As I suspected. Hector?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克和我建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank and I propose this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們加入一項簡單多數條款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We include a super majority point of order
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年內不再就這個問題進行新的立法討論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}against revisiting the issue for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白紙黑字寫下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have it in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達成一項長期的嚴肅承諾  不會被撤銷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A serious, long-term commitment with no opportunity to dismantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是加在其他要求之上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's on top of everything else we asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退伍軍人事務管理局和聯邦救災署的經費維持不變\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}VA services and FEMA stay at current levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他機構的經費削減為你提議的80%到100%\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything else at 80 to 100 percent of the cuts you propose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你贏了  柯蒂斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You get your win, Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只想避免災難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We just avoid disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許國家應該見識一下災難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe the country needs to see what disaster looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶黨的影響力很大  而你又為他們宣傳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Tea Party has a strong voice, and you're its bullhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的人民看到  這份影響力能決定法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Show your people that voice can translate into law
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不僅僅是激昂的口號\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and not just add to the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15年內不得重談  10年不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}15 years before revisitation. Not 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們通過法案後  眾議院沒有通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if the House fails to pass the bill after we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得公開譴責你們黨派造了這種僵局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you go on record blaming your own party for the gridlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就算達成協議了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I believe we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我關...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I'll turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別  很好聽  我能聽嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it's nice. Can I listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的耳朵很乾淨  我保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My ears are clean. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真美  -是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It's beautiful. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好哀傷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我放鬆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It helps me relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很辛苦嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Long day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在客服中心上班\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I work at a call center.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小時打電話給200個陌生人  是挺辛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, yeah. 200 strangers an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不打擾你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大概也不想再和陌生人聊天了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You probably don't want to talk to another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  你不掛我電話就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It -- it's all right. As long as you don't hang up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會和他們聊天嗎  那些陌生人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you ever just talk to them? The strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不允許\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not allowed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了我  肯定想問問他們是什麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I would want to do is ask them about who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  你做什麼工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about you? What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...在書店和託兒所上班\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I, um, I work at the bookstore and the daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}冬離友誼會  通往平靜之路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人第一次給我宣傳冊時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had that same look on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.39,0:24:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這個表情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the first time somebody handed me one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...不信教\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm -- I'm just -- I'm not religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著吧  看不看都無所謂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just keep it. Check it out, or don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們那兒有非常棒的音樂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got really good music there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm -- thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.13,0:24:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾議院向參議院提交了一份法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The House sent a bill to the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和弗蘭克期待的反饋完全不同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What Frank wants to send back bears zero resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是兩黨聯合的  不像我們的這份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it's bipartisan. Unlike ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著像弗蘭克的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That sounds like something Frank would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.45,0:24:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你辦公室的常客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He has a desk in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果法案在參議院通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If this bill passes in the Senate --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.77,0:24:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.06,0:24:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得有所準備  鮑勃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should be prepared, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.78,0:25:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就拭目以待了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm prepared to wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.07,0:25:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午愉快  女士們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have a good afternoon, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.44,0:25:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Ladies"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.50,0:25:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他受到了威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.43,0:25:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢豬一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.48,0:25:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他點時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give him time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.98,0:25:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前他身邊有兩個中年白人男子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He used to have two white middle-aged guys at his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.19,0:25:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在他只能依靠一個黑人和一個小他20歲的女人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now he's got a black guy and a woman 20 years his junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.04,0:25:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可這女人會開槍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who knows how to shoot a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得繼續勸他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We just need to keep at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱特琳娜·羅德里格斯在四號線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Catalina Rodriguez is on line four.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.92,0:25:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.03,0:25:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱特琳娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Catalina.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.10,0:25:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德告訴我是你幹的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ted told me it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.99,0:25:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我在聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.83,0:25:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體對我們窮追不捨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The press won't leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們連續幾周跑過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For weeks they're showing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.33,0:25:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想拍到我和艾米莉的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}trying to get pictures of me and Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.55,0:25:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我洩的密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.95,0:25:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're the only one who knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.52,0:25:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道事情怎麼會洩露\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do-- I don't know how the story got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.56,0:25:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德何必對我撒謊呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would Ted lie abut that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:25:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  也許他感到羞愧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Maybe -- maybe he's ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.53,0:26:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦  他們什麼時候才會放過我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what do I do? When will they leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  凱特琳娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I don't know, Catalina.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了這樣的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  我不知該說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm s-- I'm sorry. I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How -- how is Emily doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱特琳娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Catalina?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.06,0:26:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自信滿滿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.47,0:26:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但他有那個本事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but does he have what it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.05,0:26:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他拿出媒體方案就知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll see when I get his media plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.61,0:26:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他個性如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about his personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.76,0:26:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷人  直接  思維縝密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Charming. Direct. Very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.53,0:26:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找到了86年我們第一次一起接受採訪的錄影\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He found our first interview together, in '86.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.30,0:26:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想重溫一下  他有副本嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would love to see that. Does he have a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.10,0:26:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒有  電視臺只允許他在臺裡看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think so. The TV station made him watch it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.81,0:26:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該錄下來給總統和第一夫人看的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should screen that for the president and the first lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.39,0:26:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們學學怎麼接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Show 'em how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.89,0:26:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.64,0:27:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.52,0:27:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有注意到她和總統有什麼不正常\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you noticed anything strange between her and the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.58,0:27:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我在走道裡碰見他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I passed them in the hall yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.15,0:27:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們看上去  我說不好  很親密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And they seem -- I don't know -- very intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.99,0:27:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預備會議上他們是挺熱絡的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They did seem cozy at the prep session.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.17,0:27:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.28,0:27:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不一定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.57,0:27:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這想法挺有意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An interesting thought, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.85,0:27:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry to interrupt, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.80,0:27:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在吃午飯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.86,0:27:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨人變卦了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Republicans are backing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.24,0:27:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門多薩的幕僚長給我提了醒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mendoza's chief of staff just gave me the heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上幫我接門多薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get Mendoza on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.50,0:27:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是柯蒂斯·哈斯  他臨陣退縮了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's Curtis Haas. He got cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,籠子  差不多像那樣  不過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cages. It's really kinda like but,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.60,0:27:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但大家會看  挺逗的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you know, people look at 'em. It's kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.04,0:27:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到你郵件了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got your email.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.89,0:27:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在有空嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.83,0:27:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我過會兒打給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, sure. Can I call you right back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.83,0:27:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想問什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What exactly did you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.63,0:27:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在做網路戰的後續報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're doing some follow-up pieces on the cyber warfare thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想問問內行人知不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to get a layman's understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.06,0:27:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人會如何越過防火牆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of how the Chinese might get through a firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺複雜的  不過我可以演示下基本原理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a bit complicated, but I could show you the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.31,0:27:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那足夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.10,0:28:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}輸入響應碼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.35,0:28:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們使用的是標準多層體繫結構\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We use a standard N-tier architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.98,0:28:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像多層麵包做成的大三明治\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Think of it like a big sandwich with layers of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每層之間夾著生菜  番茄  烤牛肉之類的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Between each is the lettuce, the tomato, the roast beef, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.54,0:28:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在輸入的是組織程式碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I'm pulling up here is the org code,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.24,0:28:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離了資料庫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which, uh, separates the database --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.00,0:28:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死  我忘了馬上要和銷售部門開會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shit. I forgot there's a meeting with sales in a couple minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.80,0:28:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想晚點繼續嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to do this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.56,0:28:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我現在跑過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I'll just run over
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.72,0:28:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們說我要晚幾分鐘到  馬上回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and let them know I'll be a few minutes late. Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.83,0:28:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cool. I'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.94,0:28:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我拿到手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.17,0:28:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}很好  發送請求密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.25,0:28:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.80,0:28:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.18,0:29:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.31,0:29:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回覆啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.32,0:29:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我進去了  幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.53,0:29:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}晚上9點  西北區  哥倫比亞街  6697號見
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.75,0:29:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}切記
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.32,0:29:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}刪除簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.55,0:29:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.70,0:29:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.92,0:29:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找不著手機了  真奇怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can't find my phone. It -- it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.41,0:29:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還在的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had it just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  不好意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here it is. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.00,0:29:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.31,0:29:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個多層體繫結構\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So the, uh, N-tier architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.05,0:29:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛說的那個高科技三明治\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The high-tech sandwich I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.64,0:29:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為門多薩願意合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought Mendoza was willing to work with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.55,0:30:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是願意  問題在柯蒂斯·哈斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He is. The problem is Curtis Haas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.62,0:30:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And have you spoken with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.20,0:30:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他辦公室不回我們電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His office isn't returning our calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門多薩也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Neither is Mendoza's --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該讓步的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should've stuck to my guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午才開始投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vote isn't until tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.46,0:30:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一早就會聯繫門多薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll reach out to Mendoza first thing in the --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.99,0:30:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是國情諮文  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is the State of the Union, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能陷入尷尬境地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't be left in limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.60,0:30:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們得重寫演講\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we need to start rewriting that speech now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一分鐘也不想耽誤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to waste a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.98,0:30:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能扭轉局面  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can turn this around, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.86,0:30:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德告訴我這是你的點子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, Raymond told me this was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出妥協\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To pursue this compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是提出建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I suggested it as an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.85,0:30:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說是你逼他蹚這渾水的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said you bullied him into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他認為這是個錯誤的決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that he thought it was a -- a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.98,0:30:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他這麼反對  他就應該勸阻你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he felt so strongly, he should have advised you otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.57,0:30:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德不是政客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond is not a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.11,0:30:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他依賴於我們的政治意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He relies on our political expertise
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.10,0:30:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我們依靠他的商業頭腦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as much as we rely on his business acumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.17,0:30:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們應該到真出現問題再相互指責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe we shouldn't point fingers until there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.95,0:30:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你管這不叫問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, you wouldn't call this a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.38,0:30:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成為問題之前解決掉就不是問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if it's solved before it becomes one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是個能管理好國會的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You see, I wanted a Vice President who can manage Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.88,0:30:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是個不自量力的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not one who bites off more than he can chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.04,0:31:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就相信你做出了正確的決定  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then have faith you made the right choice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.27,0:31:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的信念正在迅速地消失殆盡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever faith I have is quickly evaporating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.71,0:31:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別給政府丟臉  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't humiliate the administration, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.72,0:31:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是其中一員了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're part of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.22,0:31:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.58,0:31:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.32,0:31:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接內線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me the private line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.65,0:31:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克擋我道  古德溫對我窮追不捨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk is blocking my way. Goodwin at my heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.95,0:31:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在一步也不能錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There can be no false steps now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越往上爬  爾虞我詐越多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The higher up the mountain, the more treacherous the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.29,0:31:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯·古德溫去找她了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas Goodwin went up to visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能也會來找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They may be looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.41,0:31:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人找過我  應該沒人知道我在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody's contacted me. I don't think anyone knows I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.15,0:31:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們要確保你不會被人發現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we need to make sure it stays that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.45,0:31:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避免不必要的交談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't speak to anyone you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去不必要的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't go anywhere you don't need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.68,0:31:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你聽到我說的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me you heard what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.85,0:31:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了  我知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I heard you. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.95,0:32:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.77,0:32:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-敷點冰  -我說了我沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Put some ice on it. - I said it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.10,0:32:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還翻我的垃圾嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What, are you going through my garbage now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.39,0:32:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公交上別人給我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone gave it to me on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.09,0:33:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人聯繫你  就來告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You let me know if anyone contacts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.41,0:33:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我來晚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.52,0:33:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.71,0:33:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你要紋多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much more you want to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.83,0:33:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,填滿這一塊嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fill in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.65,0:34:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  然後下面再多加一個罌粟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. And, uh, one more poppy down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.24,0:34:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次做這麼多啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a lot for one sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.39,0:34:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.18,0:34:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.83,0:34:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就走嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're heading in?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.05,0:34:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門多薩起的早\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mendoza's an early riser.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會解決好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.87,0:34:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得證明副總統不吃素的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to prove what the Vice President is capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.41,0:34:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別向他們證明  向我證明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't prove it to them. Prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.06,0:35:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂斯抓著我的要害  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Curtis has me by the tea bags, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.79,0:35:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒他我的黨派就要亂套\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't have a working majority without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.27,0:35:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可他不是多數黨領袖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wasn't elected leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.93,0:35:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯  但我也得選邊站\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}True. But I have to pick my battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.94,0:35:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是在預算問題上無法控制他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you can't control him on budgetary issues --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.79,0:35:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是他  還有聽命於他的15個參議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not just him. It's the 15 senators he has under his thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.79,0:35:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒他們支援我就不能連任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't be the leader next year if they turn on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.63,0:35:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想我們求他  把他找來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So he wants to be courted. Sit him down --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.45,0:35:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過和他談了  但他不肯讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already tried talking to him. He wouldn't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.51,0:35:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們一起去跟他談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we'll both talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.63,0:35:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經表明立場了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's made his position clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都在這張桌子旁握手了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We all shook hands at this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.89,0:35:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最多只能保證限制替代修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The most I can do is put the substitute amendment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.37,0:35:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表決前的辯論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the floor with limited debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.11,0:35:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們那邊公開怎麼說隨你們便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, your people can say whatever they want for the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.12,0:35:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們會投票否決修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we're gonna vote the amendment down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.45,0:35:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對象徵性姿態不敢興趣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am not interested in symbolic gestures.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.57,0:35:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能做到這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all I can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.78,0:35:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的勇氣哪去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's your courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.95,0:35:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我權力有限  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My power has limits, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.76,0:35:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再有五個共和黨人  你那票就定勝負了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Five Republicans makes you the deciding vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.77,0:35:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在很難說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, it's highly doubtful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.21,0:35:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能不能讓他們違反黨派意志投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can get them to vote against their own party.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.75,0:35:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們可以棄權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But they might abstain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那需要10人棄權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd need 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福利問題是共和黨人的長期追求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Entitlement is the Republicans' white whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.99,0:35:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至少能說通兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can get at least two of 'em to flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.59,0:35:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就只需要六票棄權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you'd only need six abstaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.34,0:36:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克森已經在打電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Erikson's already making calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.64,0:36:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donner?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.40,0:36:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有普拉斯科\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Pulaski.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.12,0:36:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我一份名單  我找幾個人一起上陣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. Get me a call list so I can tag-team with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.34,0:36:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.31,0:36:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得使狠招\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to get medieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.82,0:36:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說議會程式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When it comes to parliamentary procedure,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.01,0:36:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪條規定我不知道  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there's not a rule I don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.52,0:36:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我找到能鑽空子的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Find me the ones we can bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.07,0:36:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克  你是個明白人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mark, you're a sensible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.69,0:36:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道  我懂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I -- I know -- I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.10,0:36:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果  跟你說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if -- tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.74,0:36:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你選區內的兩家退伍軍人醫院  對  兩家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if both VA hospitals in your district -- yes, both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.43,0:36:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別掛  誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold on. Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.88,0:36:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫里亞蒂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.50,0:36:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應給他的牲牛研究中心撥款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promised him an amendment for his bovine research center.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.03,0:36:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就有六票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That makes six.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.84,0:36:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克  如果我能給兩家醫院提供資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mark, if I can get you funding for both,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.14,0:36:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願跟我們合作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}are you with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.98,0:36:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這幾天來白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You come by the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.81,0:36:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我共進午餐吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and have lunch with me sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.63,0:36:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  數目夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bye-bye. We have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.73,0:36:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打斷點名之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Once you break the quorum call
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.25,0:36:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有些麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's gonna be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.35,0:36:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們路上說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.49,0:36:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.62,0:36:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們票數可能不佔多數  -什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We might not have a majority. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主黨在挖牆腳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Dems are poaching people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.82,0:36:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納  普拉斯基  可能還有別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donner, Pulaski. Maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.55,0:36:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投票通過修正案嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Voting for the amendment?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部分支援  其餘棄權  我還在查是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some. Others abstaining. I'm still trying to figure out who.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得推遲  弄清到底是怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to delay and figure out what the fuck's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.30,0:37:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點名  離休會還有49小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quorum call. There's 49 hours until the recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小時叫一個人來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We call a name an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.30,0:37:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾文戴爾先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Avendale?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.55,0:37:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.72,0:37:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你坐了我的位置\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me. I do believe you're sitting in my chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.32,0:37:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德魯裡先生  現在進行到哪裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Drewry, what is the order of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.75,0:37:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在點名  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We are in a quorum call, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼不點名呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why aren't you calling the roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在點名  先生  不著急\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We are, sir. In a deliberate manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.05,0:37:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度快點吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's speed it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.88,0:37:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.14,0:37:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.84,0:37:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作再快點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More expeditious than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.59,0:37:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-博爾先生  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Burr? - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.82,0:37:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-坎特維爾女士  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Ms. Cantwell? - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.22,0:38:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西里尼先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Cerini?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.94,0:38:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康維爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cornwall?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.69,0:38:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.24,0:38:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科森先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Colson?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.65,0:38:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道斯特女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Douster
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.51,0:38:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法定人數夠了  我們票數不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They have a quorum. We don't have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.03,0:38:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去  讓我們的人都出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Out. Let's get all our people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.59,0:38:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-達默爾先生  達令先生  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Demerell. Mr. Darling. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.21,0:38:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-達斯瓦尼先生  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Daswani. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.82,0:38:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-唐納先生  -再快點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Donner. - Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.35,0:38:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道本先生  德懷爾先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Dobben, Mr. Dwyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.34,0:38:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-埃倫伯格  安格  艾瑞克森  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Erinburgh, Engel, Erikson. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.20,0:38:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德  法瑞森  詹特里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feld, Ferrison, Gentry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.17,0:38:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Haas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-懷特豪斯先生  -到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Whitehouse. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維克先生  懷登先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wicker. Mr. Wyden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.46,0:38:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生  沒有達到法定人數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, a quorum is not present.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.79,0:38:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席允許少數黨領袖  艾瑞克森先生發言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chair recognizes the minority leader, Mr. Erikson.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.82,0:38:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.12,0:38:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提議命令警衛官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I move to direct the sergeant at arms
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.07,0:38:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強制缺席參議員到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to compel the attendance of absent Senators;
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.83,0:39:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於無故缺席的所有參議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that warrants for the arrests of all senators not sick nor excused
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.04,0:39:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請會議主席簽發逮捕令予以逮捕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}be issued under the signature of the presiding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.38,0:39:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對動議進行表決  同意者說"贊成"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The question is on the motion. All those in favor say "Aye"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.14,0:39:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.77,0:39:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對者說"反對"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All those opposed, "Nay."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.14,0:39:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意者佔多數  動議通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The ayes have it, and the motion is agreed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.53,0:39:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我命令警衛官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The sergeant of arms is hereby instructed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.12,0:39:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強制缺席參議員到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to compel the attendance of absent senators.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.42,0:39:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回國會的感覺真好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It feels good to be back in Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在民主黨人已經授予國會警察\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Democrats have now empowered the Capitol Police
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.89,0:39:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在必要時逮捕缺席參議員的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to arrest absent members if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.65,0:39:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨參議員柯蒂斯·哈斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}According to Republican Senator Curtis Haas,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.77,0:39:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福利改革修正案的堅決反對者之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}one of the staunchest opponents of the entitlement amendment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.84,0:39:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說道  副總統正在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the vice president is, quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.28,0:39:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"用暴政取代民主\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Replacing democracy with tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.20,0:39:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經將參議院變成了國會裡的極權國家"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's transformed the Senate into a police state within the Capitol."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.86,0:39:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.46,0:39:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在想躲避媒體更難了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It'll be even harder to stay out of the news now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.29,0:39:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼還要一起接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why the joint interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.71,0:39:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又看了一遍南卡羅來納的採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I watched the South Carolina one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.02,0:39:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說服他們給了我一份拷貝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Convinced them to make me a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.92,0:40:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常有感染力  給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's powerful. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.97,0:40:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你可能想留一份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought you might want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採訪中有一個瞬間  你用手幫他捋頭髮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a moment where you ran your fingers through his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常親密  非常有人情味\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's intimate and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.72,0:40:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單是那一個瞬間就足以讓我為你丈夫投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That moment alone would've made me want to vote for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.65,0:40:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的小事  能給你幾個月的清淨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something like that will buy you months of flying beneath the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.51,0:40:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓誰來進行採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And who do you have in mind to conduct the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.15,0:40:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這代表我被錄用了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does this mean I have the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.31,0:40:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這代表你還沒出局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It means you still haven't been ruled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.81,0:40:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就當是有進步了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll consider that progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是民主黨議員的衣帽間  赫克特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is the Democratic cloak room, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.49,0:40:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的在另一邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yours is on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.84,0:40:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的招數不會成功的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you're doing won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.44,0:41:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能會  所以你大老遠的跑過來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might. Which is why you made the long walk over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.12,0:41:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ice water?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.02,0:41:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人正坐著各種交通工具趕過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have my people in planes, trains, and automobiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.58,0:41:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只需要六票達到法定人數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I need is six to make my quorum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想我有26票能幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Think what I can do with 26 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.93,0:41:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我都有45票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I've got 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.70,0:41:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人再怎麼趕也沒這麼快吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You won't be able to get your planes and trains back here fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.72,0:41:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願賭一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll roll those dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.53,0:41:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會議警衛官的工作做得非常好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The sergeant at arms is very good at his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.00,0:41:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣正可以讓柯蒂斯明白  究竟誰是老大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this is a perfect way to show Curtis who's in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.45,0:41:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在幫你  赫克特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm doing you a favor, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.28,0:41:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你想要什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.84,0:41:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要的東西  我們達成的協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I've always wanted. The package we shook hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.14,0:41:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就把參議院還給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I'll give you your Senate back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.97,0:41:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不能自願回來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can't come back voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.49,0:41:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選六個演技最好的出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pick your six best actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.49,0:41:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能妥協  赫克特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't give in, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.99,0:41:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你按黨派路線走  我們就不會落到這個境地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't be in this situation had you towed the party line.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.10,0:41:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門多薩先生到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Mendoza is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.84,0:41:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示抗議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Under protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.40,0:41:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康維爾女士到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Cornwall is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.68,0:41:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示抗議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Under protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.24,0:42:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厄爾曼先生到場  沃爾什先生到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Ullman is present. Mr. Walsh is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.39,0:42:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道斯特女士到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Douster is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.59,0:42:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯先生到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Mr. Haas is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.57,0:42:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席先生  法定人數已經夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, a quorum is now present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.71,0:42:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你通過修正案吧  我會阻撓主法案的通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can pass the amendment. I'll just filibuster the main bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.60,0:42:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.74,0:42:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我會不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.81,0:42:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管我特別想看你憋兩天尿的樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As much as I'd like to see you hold your piss for two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.80,0:42:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們已經和赫克特達成協議了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we struck a deal with Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.42,0:42:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替代修正案通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The passage of the substitute amendment
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.04,0:42:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主法案就也通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}constitutes passage of the main bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我並不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't informed of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.43,0:42:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多留意小字附條款  柯蒂斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pay attention to the fine print, Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.42,0:42:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這比協議本身重要的多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's far more important than the selling price.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.90,0:42:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻點名投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want an immediate call of the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一秒鐘時間都不要浪費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't let half a second pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.48,0:42:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.49,0:42:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法定人數已經夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A quorum is present.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.04,0:42:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於採納HR 934號法案的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The question is on the adoption of the substitute
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.06,0:42:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替代修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}amendment to HR 934.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.11,0:42:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成或是反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The yeas and nays have been ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.37,0:42:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書記官將開始點名投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the clerk will call the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.87,0:42:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯納先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Abner?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.85,0:42:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.45,0:42:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾文戴爾先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Avendale?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.60,0:42:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.15,0:42:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.06,0:42:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想為HR 934號法案提出一項修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to propose an amendment to HR 934
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.12,0:42:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯先生  請不要破壞秩序  點名投票已經開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Haas, you are out of order. The roll call has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.53,0:42:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書記官將會繼續進行點名投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The clerk will continue to call the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.36,0:42:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗先生  博爾先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Brown? Mr. Burr?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.27,0:42:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.99,0:42:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坎特維爾女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Cantwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.80,0:42:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.46,0:42:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西里尼先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Cerini?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.69,0:42:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.58,0:42:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.19,0:42:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康維爾女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Cornwall?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.09,0:42:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.84,0:42:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科森先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Colson?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.11,0:44:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興你能來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.54,0:44:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.37,0:44:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.80,0:44:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音樂非常美妙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The music was really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.34,0:44:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你想的不一樣嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not what you expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.78,0:44:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道會是什麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't sure what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.13,0:44:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫麗薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.96,0:44:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.29,0:44:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我們裡面有餅乾和蛋糕  如果你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. We've got cookies and cake inside, if you...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.51,0:44:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我還是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.36,0:44:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想見見我的一些朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you want to meet some of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.14,0:44:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-行啊  好  -行嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Okay. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.27,0:44:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-行  -走吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.18,0:44:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該把"奇蹟創造者"寫進你的簡歷  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should add "Miracle worker" to your resume, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.53,0:44:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒路的魔術倒是精彩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lazarus makes for a good magic act,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.53,0:44:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}聖經故事:馬大和馬利亞的兄弟  死後4天耶穌使他復活
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.19,0:44:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果那混蛋當初沒死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but life would have been a lot easier
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.57,0:44:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日子會輕鬆得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if the bastard hadn't died in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.55,0:44:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統本來要發脾氣  但我安撫住他了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president wanted to go ballistic, but I calmed him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.97,0:44:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說  別擔心  弗蘭克會解決問題的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said, "Don't worry. Frank'll pull this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.00,0:44:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我不會責怪你兩面派  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you? I don't blame you for being two-faced, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.26,0:44:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是厲害的政治手腕  但不能被人發現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's good politics, as long as you don't get caught at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.14,0:45:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克  如果你認為我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, Frank, if you think that I --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.43,0:45:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  雷蒙德  主會原諒你  晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's okay, Raymond. Jesus forgives you. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.45,0:45:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.41,0:45:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.41,0:45:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想來點酒嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Care for some wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.43,0:45:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Step in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.28,0:45:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近一點  再近一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Closer. Closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說一下你的名字和日期\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}State your name and the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.61,0:46:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  為什麼  我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait, why? I --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.32,0:46:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說一下你的名字和日期\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}State your name and the date, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.51,0:46:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯·古德溫  2月13日\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas Goodwin. February 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.00,0:46:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.66,0:46:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2014年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}2014.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.51,0:46:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在或曾經在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you currently or have you ever been a member of the --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.96,0:46:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What -- what -- what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.66,0:46:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在或曾經在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you currently or have you ever been a member
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.24,0:46:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,執法機構工作過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of any law enforcement agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.25,0:46:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經告訴過你我沒有了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already told you I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.54,0:46:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩步驗證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two-step verification.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒有  以前也沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not. And I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.76,0:46:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在或曾經向執法機構\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you currently or have you ever been
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.94,0:46:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提供過情報嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}an informant for law enforcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.32,0:46:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.00,0:46:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得自己被跟蹤了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think you might have been followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去幾周發生過什麼奇怪的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything strange the past few weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.46,0:46:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...你知道嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Th-- this is -- you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.32,0:46:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我很不舒服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is making me feel uncomfortable --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.16,0:46:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是鬧著玩的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not fucking around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.11,0:46:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你認為聯調局沒查過你的郵件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you think the FBI hasn't been tracking your posts,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.16,0:46:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就太天真了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then you're naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.76,0:46:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他們知道我的身份嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think they know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.88,0:46:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  你隱藏得很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. You hid yourself well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.62,0:46:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要對《先驅報》做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you going to do with the Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.82,0:46:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.69,0:46:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼想要訪問許可權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why did you want access?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.14,0:46:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有訪問許可權了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already had access.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.33,0:46:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這樣聯繫你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's how I contacted you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.86,0:46:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想知道你是不是來真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just needed to know if you were serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.28,0:47:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是腰果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's Cashew.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.45,0:47:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要聯繫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why did you contact me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.62,0:47:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你走投無路了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.71,0:47:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡當局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm not fond of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.85,0:47:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天  在安德伍德副總統的主持下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just today, under the leadership of Vice President Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.63,0:47:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,參議院通過了HR 934號法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the Senate passed HR 934,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.83,0:47:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時通過了一個歷史性的福利改革修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}along with an historic entitlement reform amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.07,0:47:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過將正常退休和提早退休的年齡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}By raising the retirement age to 68 and 65
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.92,0:47:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分別提高到68和65歲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for normal and early retirement, respectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.05,0:47:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將確保未來幾代人的福利得到保障\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we will ensure entitlements for generations to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.91,0:47:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾周後  等眾議院通過這項法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when the House passes that bill in a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.13,0:47:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對此我完全有信心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as I fully expect it to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.10,0:47:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能結束政府的開銷凍結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we will put the government freeze to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.63,0:47:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將繼續為我們的國家服務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We will continue the business of serving our country,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.12,0:48:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是讓國家癱瘓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}rather than paralyzing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.47,0:48:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是美國人民應得的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The American people deserve no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.18,0:48:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們站在民主的聖壇上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We stand at the altar of democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.00,0:48:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們站在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let us stand together.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟傑姬談過  我會在眾議院支援你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Jackie. You have my support in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.58,0:48:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在眾議院還沒通過呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it hasn't passed the House yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.72,0:48:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在交給總統前  還長路漫漫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a long march before it arrives on the president's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.47,0:48:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於我  我以前總在鏡頭邊緣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As for me, I used to be on the edge of the frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.28,0:48:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有三英尺遠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I'm only three feet away.
